　國　 110　　年　　2 　　月　　19　　日\r\n                              書記官  鍾明智","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/110%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c624%2c20210317%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,110,交簡,624,20210317,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"624","JDATE":"20210317","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}